title: Dove | 60th Birthday #RaiseTheBeautyBar
description: For the last 60 years, Dove Beauty Bar’s superior formula has remained unchanged. But when it comes to beauty, everything changed. Let’s keep redefining beauty for the next 60 years. Tell us: How will you continue to #RaiseTheBeautyBar?

transcripts: Over the past 60 years, Dove beauty bars superior formula has remained unchanged, but when it comes to beauty, everything changed. Together we redefined beauty and said no to stereo types and yes to every type. We let go of judgments and embraced what makes us unique. We're proud to have been there with you. Caring for you every step of the way. He're to the next 60 years.
